{"abstract": "We introduce a novel algorithmic approach to content recommendation based on adaptive clustering of exploration-exploitation \"bandit\") strategies. We provide a sharp regret analysis of this algorithm in a standard stochastic noise setting, demonstrate its scalability properties, and prove its effectiveness on a number of artificial and real-world datasets. Our experiments show a significant increase in prediction performance over state-of-the-art methods for bandit problems.", "referenced_work_ids": ["e6ca183bd0ab0e62c1d7c0e693bbb2869e9a3343", "023da3a9e215dadaf3d836b62b36ec895d68687b", "084e3fd4d9f0e851f2f52e4b1047c47552642a97", "d707502c9257ad843fb9dea35664c0c98b3ea4f7", "0b9f104c75fe9cba2fdb5c5d02033df94d71995f", "b0854df70e503a9c26dc0035173c8fa0686ba999", "d8ebff25a070e1785e8625b8ce4755489d1d561d", "a05da3a9fee38d2c81216bf5b24ba50c84f7d9bc", "f2d93f8ef8ca7a9b0c78c4edd4200f24197d1a66", "c2c610df7be0e49becedc9cd3e7342662e6ad73b", "36fcc0a6589ca39d30c605aae400e074dc1b1ebe", "3ee657576bc9789e13dbcfa00e8fbd21b453c763", "9e29074cc83d34e014deefe4692a37c838e2a5b1", "67f08d7baf065fe238e418f1a6816e57f55971f8", "9973d468d20cb75aa90d6ec82e1190dea4725fbf", "6bea71fa6deb19c67e9586428f8f240e789fb3df", "5e5cd8662d4661034e0c8f75cb0833d0959b4eef", "06322abde2b3411fac5bcfb7187e75f7df82d05e", "c8d7fe6495e020c879e222afa1d794cbec58ed29", "3f1d146ff1a5b84205783d1b59a803ecce5f4c41", "7adf76bdc94f3a9054187c96fe7a2c34cbebf354", "d6554953543050bba991c58dc637f10fc2474e6e", "ec0072bc37f83f1a81459df43289613e04cc61e1", "56eb0828f8e522d471d12cd62170d77a2cdfaa41", "8d2820ac17ff3cedf59f173b16b98872848bf3ad", "9a5cdfaf0968a908f167bc2c9c073cb5b56f08b3", "969bed9ece961c2e7321d205d1cfa85f03a6e477", "103f6fe35033f9327611ddafde74a2b544072980", "1e1d35136b1bf3b13ef6b53f6039f39d9ee820e3", "3b86e1d7b80d7e3a6e3f931e1b0d3d7d2118bb0d", "f2c1830eedc095b92a78dc3afa39a36343ed81ad", "af76fba5018ab3e99bed305853a94d4cd139f7a1", "4c9e36a0dbdc3e7b20e38bd288a804c05c77e9fa", "9dc8e409b6e9cc8bcab713ec7